OL,3,CWhy is Staffordshire's water supply
OL,4,Cunder pressure?
OL,6,FThe surge in demand has prompted
OL,7,FSevern Trent to increase monitoring of
OL,8,Fits network and urge customers to use
OL,9,Fwater wisely.
OL,11,FEnvironment Correspondent Charlotte
OL,12,FCross reports there is "still plenty
OL,13,Fof water in reservoirs, but people are
OL,14,Fusing it faster than it can be treated
OL,15,F- demand is outpacing supply".
OL,17,FTittesworth Reservoir acts as a
OL,18,Fprimary source of public water supply
OL,19,Ffor the North Staffordshire area,
OL,20,Fincluding parts of Stoke-on-Trent and
OL,21,FLeek.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
