OL,3,CWhy is Staffordshire's water supply
OL,4,Cunder pressure?
OL,6,FDuring past acute drought periods,
OL,7,Fthese low levels have triggered
OL,8,Fseveral management actions by Severn
OL,9,FTrent Water.
OL,11,FSevern Trent Water covers a huge area,
OL,12,Fincluding mid Wales, Gloucestershire,
OL,13,FShropshire, Herefordshire,
OL,14,FWorcestershire, parts of Staffordshire
OL,15,Fand Stoke-on-Trent, Birmingham,
OL,16,FWolverhampton, Warwickshire,
OL,17,FDerbyshire, Nottinghamshire and
OL,18,FLeicestershire.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
