CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783693094
OL,3,CWhy is Staffordshire's water supply
OL,4,Cunder pressure?
OL,6,FA Severn Trent spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"We're heading into the third heatwave
OL,8,Fof the year, and this prolonged dry
OL,9,Fweather together increased demand
OL,10,Fmeans we've reached our first water
OL,11,Flevels trigger in North Staffordshire.
OL,13,F"This isn't a drought, and there are
OL,14,Fno restrictions, it means water is
OL,15,Fbeing used faster than it can
OL,16,Fnaturally be replaced.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
