PN,34905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783693094
OL,3,CWhy is Staffordshire's water supply
OL,4,Cunder pressure?
OL,6,F"We're asking people in Staffordshire
OL,7,Fto make some small changes like
OL,8,Freusing paddling pool water or keeping
OL,9,Fa jug of water in the fridge instead
OL,10,Fof running the tap for cold water, and
OL,11,Ftogether these changes can make a big
OL,12,Fdifference.
OL,14,F"By using water carefully now, it
OL,15,Fhelps to protect suppliers for
OL,16,Fcustomers and the environment all
OL,17,Fsummer.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
